      <title>诺特称欧洲央行必须密切关注供应对经济的冲击</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-28/ecb-must-take-close-look-at-supply-shocks-to-economy-knot-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲央行管理委员会委员克拉斯·诺特称，只要通胀预期保持稳定，欧洲央行就可以忽略推高价格的供给冲击，但如果存在通胀预期过度偏离的危险，欧洲央行就应该做出有力反应。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-28/ecb-must-take-close-look-at-supply-shocks-to-economy-knot-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 28 Nov 2024 13:50:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>波兰消费放缓，未来经济增长面临风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-28/polish-consumption-slows-putting-future-economic-growth-at-risk</link>
      <description><![CDATA[波兰第三季度私人消费下滑，引发人们对未来经济增长的疑虑，也增强了加快降息的理由。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-28/polish-consumption-slows-putting-future-economic-growth-at-risk</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 28 Nov 2024 13:39:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
