      <title>罗马尼亚最高法院下令重新计票总统选举</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-28/romanian-top-court-orders-a-recount-in-presidential-election</link>
      <description><![CDATA[罗马尼亚宪法法院要求对第一轮总统选举的所有选票进行重新计票，本轮选举获胜者是一位鲜为人知的亲俄候选人。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-28/romanian-top-court-orders-a-recount-in-presidential-election</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 28 Nov 2024 12:34:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>寒冷天气刺激需求，德国风力发电量却下滑</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-28/german-power-prices-jump-as-wind-generation-set-to-plunge</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于气温愈发寒冷，迫使家庭调高恒温器，德国的风力发电量预计将于周五降至几乎为零。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-28/german-power-prices-jump-as-wind-generation-set-to-plunge</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 28 Nov 2024 11:16:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
